import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' import axios from "axios"; import { TableB, TbodyB, Tdb, ThB, TheadB, TrbB, TrhB } from "../component/ui/table"; import { Input } from "../component/ui/input"; const URI = "http://localhost:8000/usuarios/" const ShowListUser = () => { const[ dataD, setData ] = useState([]) const navigate = useNavigate() useEffect(() => { getdata() }, []) const getdata = async () => { const docs = [] const res = await axios.get(URI) res.data.forEach(element => { docs.push({ 'name':element.name, 'lastName':element.Last_name, 'tel':element.tel, 'email':element.email, }) }) setData(docs) } console.log(dataD) return(<>
Nombre apellido Usuario email tel dirección acciones del usuario { dataD.map( doc => { { doc.name } { doc.Last_name } { doc.user } { doc.email} { doc.tel} { doc.andress} } )}
) } export default ShowListUser
